    <item>
      <title>私人信贷机构在印尼法庭上获得罕见胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/visi-media-s-lenders-say-judge-accepted-560-million-debt-claims-lyxxrhi4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雅加达法官裁定完全承认 PT Visi Media Asia 的私人贷款人 5.6 亿美元的索赔，允许他们参与这家陷入困境的媒体公司的债务重组，从而在印尼法庭上获得了罕见的胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/visi-media-s-lenders-say-judge-accepted-560-million-debt-claims-lyxxrhi4</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 04:48:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>供应链受创导致生产放缓，保时捷利润出现警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/porsche-cuts-full-year-revenue-forecast-on-parts-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保时捷股份公司 (Porsche AG) 股价出现有史以来最大跌幅，此前这家豪华汽车制造商下调了今年的业绩预期，并表示铝制零部件短缺可能迫使其停止生产部分车型。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/porsche-cuts-full-year-revenue-forecast-on-parts-shortage</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 22:53:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
